{"timestamp":"2026-05-24T13:31:12.661820Z","level":"info","event":"Done. Returned value was: [{'q': \"Strive for excellence, not perfection, because we don't live in a perfect world.\", 'a': 'Joyce Meyer', 'c': 80, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Strive for excellence, not perfection, because we don&#039;t live in a perfect world.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Joyce Meyer</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'The only thing worse than being blind is having sight but no vision.', 'a': 'Helen Keller', 'c': 68, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;The only thing worse than being blind is having sight but no vision.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Helen Keller</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Try not to become a man of success, but rather try to become a man of value.', 'a': 'Albert Einstein', 'c': 76, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Try not to become a man of success, but rather try to become a man of value.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Albert Einstein</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'The man who does not value himself, cannot value anything or anyone.', 'a': 'Ayn Rand', 'c': 68, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;The man who does not value himself, cannot value anything or anyone.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Ayn Rand</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'The most difficult times for many of us are the ones we give ourselves.', 'a': 'Pema Chodron', 'c': 71, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;The most difficult times for many of us are the ones we give ourselves.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Pema Chodron</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Even if our home burns down we can rebuild it. But the things that we got for nothing, we can never replace.', 'a': 'Earl Nightingale', 'c': 108, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Even if our home burns down we can rebuild it. But the things that we got for nothing, we can never replace.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Earl Nightingale</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': \"Humor isn't for everyone. It's only for people who want to have fun, enjoy life, and feel alive.\", 'a': 'Anne Wilson Schaef', 'c': 96, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Humor isn&#039;t for everyone. It&#039;s only for people who want to have fun, enjoy life, and feel alive.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Anne Wilson Schaef</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Every day do something that will inch you closer to a better tomorrow.', 'a': 'Unknown', 'c': 70, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Every day do something that will inch you closer to a better tomorrow.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Unknown</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Disobedience is the true foundation of liberty. The obedient must be slaves.', 'a': 'Henry David Thoreau', 'c': 76, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Disobedience is the true foundation of liberty. The obedient must be slaves.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Henry David Thoreau</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': \"Failure is a great teacher. If you're open to it every mistake has a lesson to offer.\", 'a': 'Oprah Winfrey', 'c': 85, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Failure is a great teacher. If you&#039;re open to it every mistake has a lesson to offer.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Oprah Winfrey</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Like it or not, this moment is all we really have to work with.', 'a': 'Jon Kabat-Zinn', 'c': 63, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Like it or not, this moment is all we really have to work with.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Jon Kabat-Zinn</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Just living is not enough... one must have sunshine, freedom, and a little flower.', 'a': 'Hans Christian Andersen', 'c': 82, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Just living is not enough... one must have sunshine, freedom, and a little flower.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Hans Christian Andersen</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Yesterday is gone. Tomorrow has not yet come. We have only today.', 'a': 'Mother Teresa', 'c': 65, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Yesterday is gone. Tomorrow has not yet come. We have only today.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Mother Teresa</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Learn only how to avoid seeking for and attaching yourselves to anything.', 'a': 'Huang Po', 'c': 73, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Learn only how to avoid seeking for and attaching yourselves to anything.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Huang Po</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Judge your success by what you had to give up in order to get it.', 'a': 'Dalai Lama', 'c': 65, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Judge your success by what you had to give up in order to get it.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Dalai Lama</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'The ego wants to go fast. The soul needs to go slow.', 'a': 'Maxime Lagace', 'c': 52, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;The ego wants to go fast. The soul needs to go slow.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Maxime Lagace</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': \"I would rather be hated for who I am than loved for who I'm not.\", 'a': 'Wayne Dyer', 'c': 64, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;I would rather be hated for who I am than loved for who I&#039;m not.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Wayne Dyer</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Confidence comes not from always being right but not fearing to be wrong.', 'a': 'Unknown', 'c': 73, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Confidence comes not from always being right but not fearing to be wrong.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Unknown</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': \"Faith is taking the first step even when you don't see the whole staircase.\", 'a': 'Martin Luther King, Jr.', 'c': 75, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Faith is taking the first step even when you don&#039;t see the whole staircase.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Martin Luther King, Jr.</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Nothing can bring you peace but yourself.', 'a': 'Dale Carnegie', 'c': 41, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Nothing can bring you peace but yourself.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Dale Carnegie</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': \"Don't cry because it's over. Smile because it happened.\", 'a': 'Dr. Seuss', 'c': 55, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Don&#039;t cry because it&#039;s over. Smile because it happened.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Dr. Seuss</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Imagination is the beginning of creation.', 'a': 'George Bernard Shaw', 'c': 41, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Imagination is the beginning of creation.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>George Bernard Shaw</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'You cannot find peace by avoiding life.', 'a': 'Virginia Woolf', 'c': 39, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;You cannot find peace by avoiding life.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Virginia Woolf</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Insanity is relative. It depends on who has who locked in what cage.', 'a': 'Ray Bradbury', 'c': 68, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Insanity is relative. It depends on who has who locked in what cage.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Ray Bradbury</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'The goal is not to be perfect by the end, the goal is to be better today.', 'a': 'Simon Sinek', 'c': 73, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;The goal is not to be perfect by the end, the goal is to be better today.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Simon Sinek</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Turn your wounds into wisdom.', 'a': 'Oprah Winfrey', 'c': 29, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Turn your wounds into wisdom.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Oprah Winfrey</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'The secret to success is to know something nobody else knows.', 'a': 'David Brinkley', 'c': 61, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;The secret to success is to know something nobody else knows.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>David Brinkley</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'The single most powerful asset we all have is our mind.', 'a': 'Robert Kiyosaki', 'c': 55, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;The single most powerful asset we all have is our mind.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Robert Kiyosaki</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'There are as many opinions as there are experts.', 'a': 'Franklin D. Roosevelt', 'c': 48, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;There are as many opinions as there are experts.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Franklin D. Roosevelt</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': \"No matter who you are, we're creatures of habit. The better your habits are, the better they will be in pressure situations.\", 'a': 'Wayne Gretzky', 'c': 124, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;No matter who you are, we&#039;re creatures of habit. The better your habits are, the better they will be in pressure situations.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Wayne Gretzky</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Without the rain there would be no rainbow.', 'a': 'Gilbert Chesterton', 'c': 43, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Without the rain there would be no rainbow.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Gilbert Chesterton</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'The first principle of success is desire.', 'a': 'Robert Collier', 'c': 41, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;The first principle of success is desire.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Robert Collier</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Everyone you admire was once a beginner.', 'a': 'Jack Butcher', 'c': 40, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Everyone you admire was once a beginner.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Jack Butcher</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'When you move beyond your fear, you feel free.', 'a': 'Spencer Johnson', 'c': 46, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;When you move beyond your fear, you feel free.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Spencer Johnson</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Insanity: doing the same thing over and over again and expecting different results.', 'a': 'Albert Einstein', 'c': 83, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Insanity: doing the same thing over and over again and expecting different results.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Albert Einstein</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Every strike brings me closer to the next home run.', 'a': 'Babe Ruth', 'c': 51, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Every strike brings me closer to the next home run.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Babe Ruth</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'You are not stuck where you are unless you decide to be.', 'a': 'Wayne Dyer', 'c': 56, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;You are not stuck where you are unless you decide to be.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Wayne Dyer</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'The question is not what you look at, but what you see.', 'a': 'Henry David Thoreau', 'c': 55, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;The question is not what you look at, but what you see.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Henry David Thoreau</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Giving back involves a certain amount of giving up.', 'a': 'Colin Powell', 'c': 51, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Giving back involves a certain amount of giving up.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Colin Powell</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': \"It's the little things done consistently over time, straight from your heart, that have the greatest impact.\", 'a': 'Unknown', 'c': 108, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;It&#039;s the little things done consistently over time, straight from your heart, that have the greatest impact.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Unknown</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Living a life that has a greater purpose and living up to it is the ultimate degree that we should strive for.', 'a': 'Gurbaksh Chahal', 'c': 110, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Living a life that has a greater purpose and living up to it is the ultimate degree that we should strive for.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Gurbaksh Chahal</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Peace begins with a smile.', 'a': 'Mother Teresa', 'c': 26, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Peace begins with a smile.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Mother Teresa</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': \"The first thing you learn in life is you're a fool. The last thing you learn in life is you're the same fool.\", 'a': 'Ray Bradbury', 'c': 109, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;The first thing you learn in life is you&#039;re a fool. The last thing you learn in life is you&#039;re the same fool.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Ray Bradbury</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': \"You do not read a book for the book's sake, but for your own.\", 'a': 'Earl Nightingale', 'c': 61, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;You do not read a book for the book&#039;s sake, but for your own.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Earl Nightingale</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Our life is what our thoughts make it. A man will find that as he alters his thoughts toward things and other people, things and other people will alter towards him.', 'a': 'James Allen', 'c': 165, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Our life is what our thoughts make it. A man will find that as he alters his thoughts toward things and other people, things and other people will alter towards him.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>James Allen</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Many a man has failed because he had his wishbone where his backbone should have been.', 'a': 'Ronald Reagan', 'c': 86, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Many a man has failed because he had his wishbone where his backbone should have been.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Ronald Reagan</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'The future is no more uncertain than the present.', 'a': 'Walt Whitman', 'c': 49, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;The future is no more uncertain than the present.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Walt Whitman</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'There is only one way to happiness and that is to cease worrying about things which are beyond the power or our will.', 'a': 'Epictetus', 'c': 117, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;There is only one way to happiness and that is to cease worrying about things which are beyond the power or our will.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Epictetus</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Through selfless service, you will always be fruitful and find the fulfillment of your desires.', 'a': 'Bhagavad Gita', 'c': 95, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Through selfless service, you will always be fruitful and find the fulfillment of your desires.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Bhagavad Gita</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'In spite of everything, I shall rise again.', 'a': 'Vincent van Gogh', 'c': 43, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;In spite of everything, I shall rise again.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Vincent van Gogh</footer></blockquote>'}]","logger":"airflow.task.operators.airflow.sdk.definitions.asset.decorators._AssetMainOperator","filename":"python.py","lineno":229}
